Description

A blog app that users can access to different parts according to their roles. (Role management)

    - Users (not logged in) can visit the website and read the blogs.
    - Bloggers can access to admin panel and can see, edit, delete own blogs and have CRUD authentrization but doesnot have CRUD power on categories
    - Superadmin has CRUD power on all blogs, categories and users.

Tasks
    1. Dependencies:
        - json-server +
        - axios
        - react router dom
        - reduc, react-redux +
            states: blogsState, categoriesState, usersState, "loginState"
        - UI: bootstrap for react, bootstarp
    3. Project Basis
